To build, run "make".
To run the included, totally inadequate test, run "make test".
To remove artifacts, run "make clean".

This should work ok on 64-bit linux (>= 2.6.18) and 64-bit macs (tested on 10.7)
It includes binaries for libevent

To use this, link in the static lib and the two relevant libevent static libs into your binary.
See the makefile.